{"tid":514172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雞軟骨冇肉？食客呻中伏　網民：下次叫走骨","createTime":"2017-12-30T09:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T10:37:33.000Z","uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d194b7a7508aaf15be1ee3740fbb84a57ec5d98","tid":514172,"uid":59550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/174021_1d8ad4869cb97d3fdebea9690bdeff3b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F174021_1d8ad4869cb97d3fdebea9690bdeff3b.jpeg&h=c3087b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼有人投訴炒貴刁竟然是辣，連雞軟骨亦不可有骨？近日有網民於社交群組「中伏飲食報料區」發貼，怒斥餐廳的炸雞軟骨沒有肉，指「舊舊都係骨」！貼文惹起網民熱議。 <br />\n<br />\n發貼者指於某日式餐廳點了一碟炸雞軟骨，但進食時發現內裏沒有肉，咬下去只有骨和炸粉，直斥「一啲肉都冇」！面對一碟只有骨的雞軟骨，他更懷疑自己中伏，希望一眾網民為其拆解疑團！ <br />\n<br />\n惟網民反應不似預期，不少人均留言斥發貼者的投訴無理，「食雞軟骨唔食骨食咩？」、「要肉食雞胸啦」；更有人指貼文「好好笑」，稱餐廳沒有做錯，「個名已經好清楚，無（冇）違反商品說明條例喎」。同時亦有人概嘆飲食業難做，「粟米班(斑)腩冇用班(斑)腩又比(畀)人話」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171226/mobile/bkn-20171226121012750-1226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171226%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171226121012750-1226_00822_001.html&d=K2ZWUtMstStDIes0vZ4PKk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=aad5fb1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171226/mobile/bkn-20171226121012750-1226_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"03f5fb9b5f31bf20f05205820a30d3f68e680d22","tid":514172,"uid":48964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"Common sense isn't common"},{"pid":"03c386aa0c3e9e64e5820975a7eff1ab23acde9d","tid":514172,"uid":143454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd78648b0561f3dddda76f5684c614a1db153b71","tid":514172,"uid":27617,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"無（冇）<br />\n肥絲黎？"},{"pid":"d932771260ccd2502f284795189e370ab2dd5911","tid":514172,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"勁喎"},{"pid":"d9e214f4c1fc3ba96f15bb590b385c0787748628","tid":514172,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"深山大野人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但又識用Facebook"},{"pid":"8c838e70b3067fc3993e64c7b0c98dd21f7d9b72","tid":514172,"uid":129931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"以為豬軟骨d fd?"}]}